{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as soon as the war ended, which I think was in May, '45, I was able to leave and start the job in the-- with the-- go to the other job.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's where I was, in London.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that time, they were-- they were sending off these rockets, these rockets called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were these-- these rockets from V-1 and V-2s, from the-- they were firing them from Germany, from Europe, into England.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and they did a lot-- a great deal of damage, a great deal of damage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on Friday afternoons, I used to go to a bathhouse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a place where you take baths, maybe-- and it had different stores, maybe hundreds of bath tubs in it with curtains around it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You paid maybe sixpence, maybe not, maybe a quarter, and you took a bath.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got a good bath there, because I was staying in-- in the-- in the boarding house, the boarding-- the apartment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was also a bath tub, but you had to keep on putting money into it all the time, the gas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it wasn't so good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was better, bigger bath.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I could thrash around in it, you know, and take my time in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was always hot water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did it every Friday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one Friday, we are getting ready for Shabbos, and so that-- only one bath a week.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 10 minutes after I left-- for some reason, I used to hang around there and thrash in the water there and splash around and just sort of hang out, stay on longer there.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
